OL,5, Thousands of Ovo and Good Energy       
OL,6, customers are to get a refund after the
OL,7, regulator found that the firms had     
OL,8, overcharged households.                
OL,10,FOfgem has ordered the energy firms to  
OL,11,Fpay a total of #4m, #2.7m of which will
OL,12,Fbe split between 18,000 homes.         
OL,14,FThe average repayment to affected Ovo  
OL,15,Fcustomers will be #181, while Good     
OL,16,FEnergy will refund #109.               
OL,18,FThe regulator said the suppliers had   
OL,19,Fcharged people above the rate allowed  
OL,20,Funder the two energy price caps.       
